result.name: Saizeriya

reviews.text: Good food, but some dishes have too much pepper. Cheap prices in general. Loved the fried chicken and popcorn shrimp.
No chocolate when I bought drink bar which was my favourite drink and only thing I can drink.
Good price & well deserving good food.

It was a newly opened branch, with the quality of food and services living up to one's expectation.  Frankly, it is always more on the 'self-service' side at all branches of this chained restaurant, but the food is always good, with great value for money.  

It is worth taking note that takeaway service is UNAVAILABLE at this particular branch, I am not sure whether it is just temporary.  There was a sign asking customers to go to their TBG Mall Branch for takeaway service.
Variety with reasonable price 👍😋

reviews.text: 平靚正，絕對食得過，可惜等位耐咗啲！
老實講，薩利亞真係食到厭厭地，不過佢啲價錢真係無得頂。係咁多間食肆中，佢真係算便，食物質素又保持到，所以每次去到都有勁多人排隊，加些少錢又可以任飲，啲位又大又舒服。
一碟意粉就飽啦（大概三十元左右）
薩莉亞 啲午餐麻麻地唔係咁好食啲嘢又唔夠熱 暖暖哋食落去 啲嘢一定要好熱先好食麻麻地呀
Good food, but some dishes have too much pepper. Cheap prices in general. Loved the fried chicken and popcorn shrimp.

result.name: Amoy Plaza

reviews.text: Old private estate shopping mall struggling to compete with new ones.  It is not the new huge malls with high ceilings big brands but you may like the surprises and the rare shops at the corners or far end of corridors.  There are a few shops selling expert model kits for adults and toys for teenagers and game console games also.
Many good restaurants, many hobby stores. Something for everyone. Best of all, affordable price.
Many delicious food such as Genki Sushi and Pizza Hut

A lot of choices to choose from, a cinema and stuff like that. What you would hope from a decent shopping mall. There are also housing estates above the shopping centre but ofc it's too expensive for a normal human being in Hong Kong to afford
Nice concentrated shops and diversity.
